- **Description Differentiation:** The main coupons list now keeps the **short summary**, while the Coupon Details page exclusively displays the **long, professional description**.
- **Collapsible Terms & Conditions:** Implemented a smooth toggle for the T&C section. It is now collapsed by default to keep the interface clean, expanding only when the user needs to see the details.
